desc
@Vplot version of sutwig - full featured wiggler
@


1.7
log
@Changed agc default to accomodate short synthetics.
@
text
@/* SUTWIG: $Revision: 1.6 $ ; $Date: 90/11/06 16:41:11 $               */

/*----------------------------------------------------------------------
 * Copyright (c) Colorado School of Mines, 1990.
 * All rights reserved.
