log
@Initial revision
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
/* SUTWIG: $Revision: 1.10 $ ; $Date: 90/06/18 18:33:45 $               */
d23 1
a23 1
SUTWIG - full-featured wiggle trace program for data plotting           \n\
d25 1
a25 1
sutwig <stdin [optional parameters] | tube                              \n\
@
